<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Hi guys.. a few questions here..<P>When engaging the big bad boy mobs such as Velk, Vindi etc...the one problem I have noticed in my guild, time and time again is the transfer of aggro to the 2nd assist once MA's defensive disc drops. In many instances 5-10 folks die before the 2nd assist can gain aggro. CH cycle gets messed up.. folks are running around waving their hands in the air screaming etc...    <IMG SRC="wink.gif" border="0"><P>Now, we are trying to implement some of the ideas in this <A HREF="http://pub29.ezboard.com/fclericsofeverquestfrm1.showMessage?topicID=471.topic" TARGET=_blank>thread</A><P>A very good read, I suggest all my cleric collegues show this to your guilds.<P>Anyhow..<BR>I was wondering if folks could share their experience with successful aggro transfer and the methodology used.<P>Thoughts comments?<P>Thanks guys for any input<P>--------------------<P>Baroness <A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=17597" TARGET=_blank>Heloisa DeusloVolt</A><BR>High Priest<BR>Cascade Point<BR>Rodcet Nife
